name: @voxxit
body:
### Docker Repositories

* `voxxit/postgresql` - [Automated Build](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/voxxit/postgresql/) - [GitHub](http://github.com/voxxit/docker-postgresql) - Builds of PostgreSQL 9.3 and 9.4 on Debian 7.4; sensibly tuned and secured for use with Rails projects of any size. 
* `voxxit/ruby` - [Automated Build](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/voxxit/ruby/) - [GitHub](http://github.com/voxxit/docker-ruby) - Ruby 2.1.x built on Debian 7.4 using ruby-install; use the RUBY_VERSION environment variable to install any version you want
* `voxxit/memcached` - [Automated Build](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/voxxit/memcached/) - [GitHub](http://github.com/voxxit/docker-memcached) - Memcached container on Debian 7.4, secured with SASL.
* `voxxit/skel` - [Automated Build](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/voxxit/skel/) - [GitHub](http://github.com/voxxit/docker-skel) - Up-to-date Debian 7.4 base box with curl, nano, git and HTTPS apt support; includes PostgreSQL PGDG and NodeSource apt repositories
